# use case diagram
Screen0
    - play
    - quit

Game screen
    - board
    - dice
    - players
    - player roll dice
    - update player position
    - if player won
        - show player won
        - display Screen0
    - switch turn

Player Won screen
    - play again
    - quit

# functional diagram
- show_screen0
- show_game_screen
- show_player_won_screen

- play

- roll_dice
- update_player_position
- check_if_won
- switch_turn
